videos.title: Render Inert and The Overlords!  Duskmourn Standard
videos.description:
Render Inert wasn't meant for battles, it was meant for all the new Overlords. We've also got Valgavoth as a sweet reanimate target in this Ozhov deck!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
